  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/9f575bbb44a52449c70d100080d796a0.avif?t=1712056283\" width=512 height=256 /></span><br><strong>《腾起之蛇现世》《Rising Snake Present World》</strong><br>It is a horror game based on Qimen Dunjia and Feng Shui, with the Nine Palaces of Qimen Dunjia as a reflection, showcasing the winding stories that take place on a real sized university campus.<br><br><strong>Game Features</strong><br>Abandoning past horror games, there are cabinets for good news and cabinets for bad news. Play this game in a combat style that aligns with China's Qimen Dunjia. The game contains a lot of professional knowledge about Qimen Dunjia, Feng Shui Kanyu, and making runes and symbols. Players who like magic can enjoy a feast of blessings, while horror game enthusiasts who do not understand magic can also play freely.<br><strong><br>The hand decision system based on the Nine Palaces includes attack spells based on the Five Acts</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/74d2cb101767d97be3485cc88f3a4670.poster.avif?t=1712056283\" width=596 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/74d2cb101767d97be3485cc88f3a4670.webm?t=1712056283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/74d2cb101767d97be3485cc88f3a4670.mp4?t=1712056283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Auxiliary Mantra adapted from Qimen Dunjia</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/6b8c2e2e1cfdacad240fe6b115184725.poster.avif?t=1712056283\" width=596 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/6b8c2e2e1cfdacad240fe6b115184725.webm?t=1712056283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/6b8c2e2e1cfdacad240fe6b115184725.mp4?t=1712056283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>In the game, some real spells have been adapted into relevant decryption games</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/29204f56e099852da49ecc06e0c43c29.poster.avif?t=1712056283\" width=596 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/29204f56e099852da49ecc06e0c43c29.webm?t=1712056283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/29204f56e099852da49ecc06e0c43c29.mp4?t=1712056283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>There are also many unique props in the game as \"helpers\" to assist players in playing</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/0386dbd64821e5e3812aebd2780237ae.poster.avif?t=1712056283\" width=596 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/0386dbd64821e5e3812aebd2780237ae.webm?t=1712056283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/0386dbd64821e5e3812aebd2780237ae.mp4?t=1712056283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Don't forget the most important Qimen Dunjia system, please look forward to the Qimen Visualization Plate at that time!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/05af572733069557f1c4497cfda2bfe9.poster.avif?t=1712056283\" width=596 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/05af572733069557f1c4497cfda2bfe9.webm?t=1712056283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/05af572733069557f1c4497cfda2bfe9.mp4?t=1712056283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>background story</strong><br>Why are the classmates' eyes so strange on a peaceful and beautiful university campus? Why are there frequent homicides on campus? Is the teacher the murderer or the student the murderer or... is it human harm, ghost harm, or ghost harm? What strange story has happened in this school? At that time, please ask all the Taoists to investigate.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/40ed62023b7a9c15b10a7c2a4da975af.avif?t=1712056283\" width=512 height=256 /></span><br>srzrhsz<br><br>----------------------------------------------------------------------<br>We are a small team of two, and due to various reasons, the process of game development has been relatively slow. But we will do our best to fix every bug, and we hope that all Taoist Priests can provide more opinions. If possible, we will also adopt it as appropriate!<br>Official QQ group：10093771",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/9f575bbb44a52449c70d100080d796a0.avif?t=1712056283\" width=512 height=256 /></span><br><strong>《腾起之蛇现世》《Rising Snake Present World》</strong><br>It is a horror game based on Qimen Dunjia and Feng Shui, with the Nine Palaces of Qimen Dunjia as a reflection, showcasing the winding stories that take place on a real sized university campus.<br><br><strong>Game Features</strong><br>Abandoning past horror games, there are cabinets for good news and cabinets for bad news. Play this game in a combat style that aligns with China's Qimen Dunjia. The game contains a lot of professional knowledge about Qimen Dunjia, Feng Shui Kanyu, and making runes and symbols. Players who like magic can enjoy a feast of blessings, while horror game enthusiasts who do not understand magic can also play freely.<br><strong><br>The hand decision system based on the Nine Palaces includes attack spells based on the Five Acts</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/74d2cb101767d97be3485cc88f3a4670.poster.avif?t=1712056283\" width=596 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/74d2cb101767d97be3485cc88f3a4670.webm?t=1712056283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/74d2cb101767d97be3485cc88f3a4670.mp4?t=1712056283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Auxiliary Mantra adapted from Qimen Dunjia</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/6b8c2e2e1cfdacad240fe6b115184725.poster.avif?t=1712056283\" width=596 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/6b8c2e2e1cfdacad240fe6b115184725.webm?t=1712056283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/6b8c2e2e1cfdacad240fe6b115184725.mp4?t=1712056283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>In the game, some real spells have been adapted into relevant decryption games</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/29204f56e099852da49ecc06e0c43c29.poster.avif?t=1712056283\" width=596 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/29204f56e099852da49ecc06e0c43c29.webm?t=1712056283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/29204f56e099852da49ecc06e0c43c29.mp4?t=1712056283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>There are also many unique props in the game as \"helpers\" to assist players in playing</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/0386dbd64821e5e3812aebd2780237ae.poster.avif?t=1712056283\" width=596 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/0386dbd64821e5e3812aebd2780237ae.webm?t=1712056283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/0386dbd64821e5e3812aebd2780237ae.mp4?t=1712056283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Don't forget the most important Qimen Dunjia system, please look forward to the Qimen Visualization Plate at that time!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/05af572733069557f1c4497cfda2bfe9.poster.avif?t=1712056283\" width=596 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/05af572733069557f1c4497cfda2bfe9.webm?t=1712056283\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/05af572733069557f1c4497cfda2bfe9.mp4?t=1712056283\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>background story</strong><br>Why are the classmates' eyes so strange on a peaceful and beautiful university campus? Why are there frequent homicides on campus? Is the teacher the murderer or the student the murderer or... is it human harm, ghost harm, or ghost harm? What strange story has happened in this school? At that time, please ask all the Taoists to investigate.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433460/extras/40ed62023b7a9c15b10a7c2a4da975af.avif?t=1712056283\" width=512 height=256 /></span><br>srzrhsz<br><br>----------------------------------------------------------------------<br>We are a small team of two, and due to various reasons, the process of game development has been relatively slow. But we will do our best to fix every bug, and we hope that all Taoist Priests can provide more opinions. If possible, we will also adopt it as appropriate!<br>Official QQ group：10093771",
